summary: I remember when we met so clearly. I was not familiar with Jodie’s work prior to [Killing Eve]. It was in this crappy studio,...
caption: I remember when we met so clearly. I was not familiar with Jodie’s work prior to [Killing Eve]. It was in this crappy studio, and then we sat down and we had a really long audition process. It was very intense and it was really, really long. And we were very open and fresh with each other. Yeah, that’s what I enjoyed about it. There wasn’t necessarily a large persona that you were familiar with.. Or expecting. It was the best.
